@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_toafpa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v1 + 0.70 * v1 + 0.51)))
    v2 = wp.exp(0.57)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.41)) + (0.85 / wp.cos(tmp + 0.74)))
    data[tid] = v0
